Program: Outlook
Title: Shafik Gabr: Bridging Divides
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0104gt7
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 5 Nov 2012
One of Egypt's most successful businessmen, Shafik Gabr, talks about how his art collection inspired him to build bridges between East and West. And Paul Shonauer, a successful policeman and a father of two on coming back to his kids and to the police force as a woman. Image: Shafik Gabr